ðŸ“š Design Patterns Used

    Pattern	            Role
    Singleton	          GameManager, AudioManager
    Command	            Extendable input actions (planned)
    Strategy	          (To be added: enemy AI behaviors)
    Factory	            (Optional for future: enemy creation)